title: The Big Allotment Challenge - Series 1 Season 1 Complete
description:
Nine pairs of the UK's best allotmenteers take part in The Big Allotment Challenge, presented by Fern Britton.

Over six weeks they are put to the test, as they attempt to harvest prize-winning fruits, vegetables and flowers for show day. Plus, their preserving skills will be tested to the limit as they are challenged to produce jams, chutneys, cordials, pickles and jellies.

All the challenges are devised by award-winning gardener Jim Buttress, international floral designer Jonathan Moseley and Queen of Preserves Thane Prince who are on hand to judge and taste their efforts.




The Big Allotment Challenge - Series 1 Complete




Original Air Dates: 15-Apr-2014 to 15-May-2014
